{"id": "1375189000700170313", "channel_id": "1326453691527594035", "author_id": "328095417436864512", "author_name": "fatewriter", "content": "There are multiple characters and wheels that can cleanse, and despite noble staff costing 5 arith it's still frequently used because it's worth it.\nDelay damage always deals more damage than normal direct damage since they can be cleansed, also shield can defend against delay damage more efficiently. Cuz you know that delay damage is gonna come at the end of the turn so you can shield accordingly and gain alimus from it while if the enemy uses direct damage he can just wait 1 turn and defend or heavy wound you for your shield to waste", "timestamp": "2025-05-22T19:10:07.543000+00:00", "type": 19, "edited_timestamp": "2025-05-22T19:13:20.681000+00:00", "mentions": ["91654723089760256"], "reply_to": "1375180060025294940"}
{"id": "1375189497653760071", "channel_id": "1326453691527594035", "author_id": "328095417436864512", "author_name": "fatewriter", "content": "Delay damage is like high risk high payout", "timestamp": "2025-05-22T19:12:06.026000+00:00"}
